      h4 Get the mobile app
      .row
        .image-container.col-md-12
          = link_to "javascipt:void(0);", class: "col-md-12" do
            = image_tag "/assets/app-icon.png", class: "pull-left footer-app-icon"
      .text-container
        p Or, enter your mobile number
        p below, and we'll send you a
        p download link via text message
    .col-md-8
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .row
